","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event243-01-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"晴海","body":"新的負責窗口好像是會跟藝人\n不斷針對細節做確認的類型，\n所以跟唱片公司的會議應該會比之前還要多","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":222,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":222,"voiceId":"event243-01-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"晴海","body":"有關第二張專輯的方針他好像也說想跟大家一起決定，\n所以最近應該會希望跟大家做個初次拜會","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":222,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":222,"voiceId":"event243-01-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"燐子","body":"跟新負責窗口的初次拜會……\n怎麼覺得有點緊張啊……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event243-01-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"亞子","body":"沒問題的喔，燐燐！　唱片公司的人，\n一定也是因為非常喜歡音樂才會選擇這間公司的對吧？\n他一定會是個好人，也可